text: Hubert-Folie is a former commune in the Calvados department in the Normandy region in northwestern France. On 1 January 2019, it was merged into the new commune Castine-en-Plaine.Arrêté préfectoral 19 December 2018, p. 10 ==Population== ==See also== *Communes of the Calvados department ==References== Category:Former communes of Calvados (department) Category:Calvados communes articles needing translation from French Wikipedia Category:Populated places disestablished in 2019
